{# Template: ensemble/standing_session_status_report.j2 #}
{# functional_role: flowdef #}
{# implementation_type: jinja2 #}
{# produces: bot_status_report #}
{# Purpose: Bot status report to standing ensemble session #}

## Status Report — {{ bot_name }}

**Timestamp:** {{ timestamp }}  
**Status:** {{ status }}  
**Uptime:** {{ uptime }}

### Metrics

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
{% for metric in metrics %}
| {{ metric.name }} | {{ metric.value }} |
{% endfor %}

### Active Issues

{% if issues %}
{% for issue in issues %}
- **{{ issue.severity }}:** {{ issue.description }}
  - First observed: {{ issue.first_observed }}
  - Occurrences: {{ issue.occurrences }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No active issues.
{% endif %}

### Recent Actions

{% for action in recent_actions %}
- {{ action.timestamp }}: {{ action.description }}
{% endfor %}

### Energy Budget

- Used: {{ energy_used }} / {{ energy_cap }}
- Remaining: {{ energy_remaining }}
- Efficiency: {{ energy_efficiency }}

---

*Automated status report from {{ bot_name }}*